{"word":"H4026 - מִגְדָּל - migdâl - mig-dawl' - Castle","slug":"H4026","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִגְדָּל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>migdâl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mig-dawl'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Castle"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D4;</bdo>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D2;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05DC; - migda&#x0302;l  migda&#x0302;la&#x0302;h</b></b> - <i>mig-dawl', mig-daw-law'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1431\">H1431</a>; a <i>tower</i> (from its size or height); by analogy a <i>rostrum</i>; figuratively a (pyramidal) <i>bed</i> of flowers: - castle, flower, pulpit, tower. Compare the names following."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1419\">H1419</a>, <a href=\"#/H1420\">H1420</a>, <a href=\"#/H1431\">H1431</a>, <a href=\"#/H1432\">H1432</a>, <a href=\"#/H1433\">H1433</a>, <a href=\"#/H1434\">H1434</a>, <a href=\"#/H1435\">H1435</a>, <a href=\"#/H1436\">H1436</a>, <a href=\"#/H1437\">H1437</a>, <a href=\"#/H3012\">H3012</a>, <a href=\"#/H4024\">H4024</a>, <a href=\"#/H4027\">H4027</a>, <a href=\"#/H4028\">H4028</a>, <a href=\"#/H4029\">H4029</a>"}]}